is, the total number of approved houses under #PMAYUrban have become 68.54 lakh. pic.twitter.com/SvKDa8jkRW\u2014 Housing For All (@PMAYUrban) December 27, 2018After subsuming projects of Rajiv Awas Yojana (RAY) Scheme, the cumulative number of houses sanctioned under PM Awas Yojana Urban (PMAY-U) is now more than 68,54,126.Approved Houses in Previous CSMC Meetings \u2013 PM Awas Yojana Urban Housing SchemeThe complete details of the total number of affordable houses sanctioned under PMAY-U in the previous meetings of central sanctioning and monitoring committee (CSMC) can be checked through the links below:-CSMC 40th Meeting \u2013 2.05 lakh more affordable houses under PM Awas Yojana UrbanCSMC 39th meeting \u2013 2.15 lakh more affordable houses under PMAY-UCSMC 38th meeting \u2013 6.28 lakh more affordable houses under PMAY-UCSMC 37th meeting \u2013 1.12 lakh more affordable houses under PMAY-UCSMC 36th meeting \u2013 2.67 Lakh more affordable houses under PMAY-UCSMC 35th meeting \u2013 3.19 lakh more affordable houses under PMAY UCSMC 34th meeting \u2013 1.5 lakh more affordable houses under PMAY UCSMC 33rd meetingCSMC 32nd meeting \u2013 3.21 lakh more affordable houses under PMAY UCSMC 31st meeting \u2013 1.28 lakh more affordable houses under PMAY UCSMC 30th meeting \u2013 1.86 lakh more affordable houses under PMAY UCSMC 29th meeting \u2013 5.45 lakh more affordable houses under PMAY UVisit the official website https://pmaymis.gov.in/ to get complete details on Pradhan Mantri Awas Yojana Urban.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}